45 void OnTriggerEnter(Collider other)

61
66 IEnumerator EnableAfterSeconds()
67 {
68 yield return new WaitForSeconds(disableTime);
69 buttonPressDisabled = false;
70 }
71
75 private void executeAction()
76 {
77 Transform target = FindObjectOfType<CaseController>().loadedPatient.transform;
78 if (target == null) return;
79
80 target.localScale += new Vector3(
81 target.localScale.x * scaleFactor,
82 target.localScale.y * scaleFactor,
83 target.localScale.z * scaleFactor
84 );
85 }
86 }
